Package akka.remote.testconductor

Class ConductorHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jboss.netty.channel.SimpleChannelUpstreamHandler
      • akka.remote.testconductor.ConductorHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.jboss.netty.channel.ChannelHandler, org.jboss.netty.channel.ChannelUpstreamHandler
    public class ConductorHandler
extends org.jboss.netty.channel.SimpleChannelUpstreamHandler
    This handler is installed at the end of the controller&rsquo;s netty pipeline. Its only purpose is to dispatch incoming messages to the right ServerFSM actor. There is one shared instance of this class for all connections accepted by one Controller.
